    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/07fcc1b255e38365779de5753ab7f74c.avif?t=1729061933\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br><i>Evergreen is a simulation game about leaving the stress of the city behind and starting a new life in a mountain valley.</i><br><br>This simulation game is meant to be a relaxing and calming experience. Forget about stressful hunger, health or temperature meters. Build your house with your own hands, collect the resources that nature provides, travel to a small village to sell what you don't need, buy supplies in stores and admire the wonders of nature.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/5d7bc699e4d750580b2ff69f53062378.webp?t=1729061933\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In the Evergreen prologue, you will be able to experience your first day in the valley. <br></li><li>The map size is limited, but the main mechanics are all there and polished. <br></li><li>Chop down trees, mine stone and start building your new home in this beautiful world. <br></li><li>Take your car and travel to a nearby town to buy some supplies or furniture to decorate your place.</li></ul><br>Don't forget to add the full game to your wishlist and visit the store page to see what is included in the complete game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/b0345dea609deaa213ae0e32b96d6608.webp?t=1729061933\" width=600 height=20 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2188880/extras/e2eb6db9ee86c121f317cf49236df401.poster.avif?t=1729061933\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://s